\c 36
\s Jehoahazi naJehoyakimu naJehoyakini madzimambo aJudha
\p
\v 1 Zvino vanhu venyika iyo vakatora Jehoahazi mwanakomana waJosiya, ndokumugadza kuva mambo pachinzvimbo chababa vake paJerusarema\x + 2 Madz. 23.30-34.\x*.
\v 2 Jehoahazi waiva nemakore makumi maviri nematatu paakava mambo, ndokutonga mwedzi mitatu paJerusarema.
\v 3 Mambo weEgipita ndokumubvisa paJerusarema, ndokuripisa nyika matarenda zana esirivha netarenda regoridhe.
\v 4 Mambo weEgipita ndokugadza Eriyakimi munin'ina wake kuva mambo pamusoro paJudha neJerusarema, ndokushandura zita rake kuva Jehoyakimu. Neko ndokutora munin'ina wake Joahazi, ndomuisa kuEgipita.
\p
\v 5 Jehoyakimu waiva nemakore makumi maviri nemashanu paakava mambo; ndokutonga makore gumi nerimwe paJerusarema; ndokuita zvakaipa pameso paJehovha Mwari wake\x + 2 Madz. 23.36,37.\x*.
\v 6 Kwakakwira kumurwisa Nebhukadhinezari mambo weBhabhironi\x + 2 Madz. 24.1. Habh. 1.6.\x*, ndokumusunga nemaketani ematare kumuisa kuBhabhironi\x + 2 Madz. 24.6.\x*.
\v 7 Nebhukadhinezari wakauisa \add imwe\add* yemidziyo yeimba yaJehovha kuBhabhironi ndokuiisa mutembere yake kuBhabhironi\x + 36.10,18. 2 Madz. 24.13. Ezi. 1.7. Dhan. 1.1,2. 5.2.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Zvino dzimwe dzenyaya dzaJehoyakimu, nezvinyangadzo zvake zvaakaita, nezvakawanikwa maari, tarirai zvakanyorwa mubhuku remadzimambo aIsraeri naJudha\x + 2 Madz. 24.5,6.\x*. Jehoyakini mwanakomana wake ndokuva mambo pachinzvimbo chake.
\p
\v 9 Jehoyakini\x + 2 Madz. 24.8,9.\x* waiva nemakore masere paakava mambo, ndokutonga mwedzi mitatu nemazuva gumi paJerusarema; ndokuita zvakaipa pameso paJehovha\x + 2 Madz. 24.8.\x*.
\v 10 Zvino pakudzoka kwegore, mambo Nebhukadhinezari\x + 2 Madz. 24.10-17.\x* wakatuma \add nhume\add* ndokuuya naye kuBhabhironi, pamwe nemidziyo inoshuvika yeimba yaJehovha\x + 36.7.\x*, ndokuita munin'ina wake Zedhekia mambo pamusoro paJudha neJerusarema\x + Jer. 37.1.\x*.
\s Zedhekia mambo wekupedzisira waJudha
\p
\v 11 Zedhekia waiva nemakore makumi maviri nerimwe paakava mambo; ndokutonga makore gumi nerimwe paJerusarema\x + 2 Madz. 24.18,19. Jer. 52.1,2.\x*.
\v 12 Zvino wakaita zvakaipa pameso paJehovha Mwari wake; haana kuzvininipisa pamberi paJeremiya muporofita, \add aitaura \add*kubva mumuromo waJehovha\x + Jer. 21.1-7. 27.12-28. 32.1-5. 37.1-10. 38.14-28.\x*.
\s Nebhukadhinezari anoputsa Jerusarema nekutapa vaJudha
\p
\v 13 Uye wakamukirawo mambo Nebhukadhinezari\x + 2 Madz. 24.20.\x* waiva amupikisa naMwari\x + Eze. 17.18.\x*; asi wakaomesa mutsipa wake\x + 30.8.\x*, ndokusimbisa moyo wake zvekuti haana kutendeukira kuna Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri\x + Det. 2.30.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Uye vakuru vese vevapristi nevanhu vakadarika zvikuru sezvinyangadzo zvese zvevahedheni, ndokusvibisa imba yaJehovha yaaiva aita tsvene paJerusarema\x + 33.23.\x*.
\v 15 Zvino Jehovha Mwari wemadzibaba avo wakatuma \add mashoko\add* kwavari neruoko rwenhume dzake\x + 24.19. Neh. 9.30.\x*, achimuka mangwanani achituma, nokuti waiva netsitsi nevanhu vake uye nenzvimbo yake yekugara.
\v 16 Asi vaiseka nhume dzaMwari\x + 30.10.\x*, ndokuzvidza mashoko ake\x + Num.. 15.31.\x*, ndokusveveredza vaporofita vake\x + Gen.. 27.12. Jer. 32.3. 38.6. Mat. 23.34-37.\x*, kusvika hasha dzaJehovha dzamukira vanhu vake, kusvika pasisina kurapika\x + Ezi. 5.12.\x*.
\v 17 Naizvozvo wakakwidza pavari mambo weVaKaradhiya\x + 2 Madz. 25.1. Det. 28.49. Ezi. 9.7.\x* uyo wakauraya majaya avo nemunondo muimba yavo tsvene; uye haana kunzwira tsitsi jaya kana musikana, munhu mukuru kana mutana\x + Map. 78.63. 79.2,3.\x*; wakapa vese muruoko rwake\x + Job. 12.12. 15.10. 29.8. 32.6.\x*.
\v 18 Nemidziyo yose yeimba yaMwari, mikuru nemidiki, nefuma yeimba yaJehovha, nefuma yamambo neyemachinda ake, zvese wakauisa kuBhabhironi\x + 36.7,10. 2 Madz. 25.13-15.\x*.
\v 19 Zvino vakapisa imba yaMwari, ndokuputsa rusvingo rweJerusarema\x + 2 Madz. 25.9. Map. 74.6,7. 79.1.\x*, nemizinda yayo yose vakapisa nemoto\x + 2 Madz. 15.25.\x*, ndokuparadza midziyo yayo yose inoshuvika\x + 32.27.\x*.
\v 20 Zvino avo vakasara pamunondo wakavatapira kuBhabhironi\x + 2 Madz. 25.11.\x*, kwavakava varanda kwaari nevanakomana vake\x + Jer. 27.7.\x*, kusvika kwava pakutonga kweushe hwePeresia\x + 36.22.\x*;
\v 21 kuzadzisa shoko raJehovha, mumuromo waJeremiya\x + Jer. 25.9,11,12. 29.10.\x*, kusvika nyika yafarira masabata ayo\x + Rev. 26.34,35,43. Dhan. 9.2. Job. 14.6.\x*; mazuva ese ekuparadzwa vakachengeta sabata, kusvika pakuzara kwemakore makumi manomwe\x + Rev. 25.4,5.\x*.
\s Koreshi mambo wePerisiya unotendera VaJudha kudzoka
\p
\v 22 Zvino mugore rekutanga raKoreshi mambo wePerisiya, kuti shoko raJehovha \add rarehwa\add* nemuromo waJeremiya ripedzisike, Jehovha akamutsa mweya waKoreshi mambo wePerisiya, wakapfuudza inzwi nepaushe hwake hwese, uyewo mukunyora, achiti:
\p
\v 23 Ndizvo zvinoreva Koreshi mambo wePerisiya: Jehovha Mwari wekumatenga wakandipa ushe hwese hwenyika, uye iye wakandiraira kumuvakira imba paJerusarema riri paJudha. Ndiani ari pakati penyu wevanhu vake vose? Jehovha Mwari wake ngaave naye, uye ngaakwire\x + Ezi. 1.1-3.\x*.